main event: On August 8, 1961, a high-speed, 90 ft long object with sharp edges was detected on radar and observed from the ground in Santa Fe, Argentina.
interesting points: The object maneuvered at high speed and was silent during its flight., After 10 minutes, the object hovered briefly before ascending again., Witnesses described the object as being operated by beings in holstered attire who seemed to be observing the craft., A subsequent report detailed a witness encountering 15 beings surrounding a metallic object., The account mentioned descriptions of the beings and the craft's characteristics resembling popular depictions of UFOs.
sighted object: a high-speed object approximately 90 ft long
witness description: the witness described encountering a group of beings around the object, resembling aliens depicted in media
